15
00:02:24,777 --> 00:02:26,240
Cigarettes!

16
00:02:27,428 --> 00:02:31,001
Marko!

17
00:02:57,195 --> 00:02:59,079
Ah!
You fool!

18
00:02:59,756 --> 00:03:01,842
I'll be right back.
Come here.

19
00:03:03,304 --> 00:03:05,104
Why didn't you tell me
you were coming?

20
